{"tid":1785684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佛教善德英文中學校長何滿添病逝　中學校長會主席：他讓學生安全表達反修例意見","createTime":"2019-12-16T14:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T16:10:47.000Z","uid":165683,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"796a70d37b4ffbd5af53faa0610b118c56901857","tid":1785684,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:37:35.000Z","msg":"佛教善德英文中學校長何滿添今日（16日）因患淋巴癌離世，終年58歲。學校於校網張貼訃告，表示何校長今日在沙田醫院因病離世，讚揚他多年來熱心教育事業，秉承校訓宗旨，積極培育人才，其鍥而不捨的精神，成為後輩學習榜樣；校監及校董會各成員、學校全體師生深表哀痛。校方將於1月4日上午10時至12時舉行追思會。<br />\n<br />\n校方接受本報查詢稱，何校長離世時，家人、教職員陪伴在側，又稱何校長早前知道自己病情不穩，故提早11月底交捧副校長，目前學校由署理校長負責工作。<br />\n<br />\nMingpao:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191216/s00001/1576488881791/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191216%2Fs00001%2F1576488881791%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7qZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=8400b9ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191216%2Fs00001%2F1576488881791%2F&h=86a78311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191216/s00001/1576488881791/</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook Post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/goldwaterhk/posts/2648229131930560?__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgoldwaterhk%2Fposts%2F2648229131930560%3F__tn__%3D-R&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7qZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=371d6fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/goldwaterhk/posts/2648229131930560?__tn__=-R</a>"},{"pid":"0d99bb949a971c3e23b3aee3e3fb2aa997377b07","tid":1785684,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/